.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, eggplant, kale, peas
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, red, orange, lilac
4 different games are played: bridge, whist, backgammon, canasta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, cycling, volleyball
 1. the person who likes lilac is in an even position##4
 2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person who likes red is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 4. the person eating eggplant is the person playing bridge##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 6. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 7. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 8. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
11. the person playing backgammon is the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | carrot  | eggplant    | kale     | peas       |
| Color         | orange | lilac | yellow   | red |
| Game   | backgammon | bridge   | whist   | canasta    |
| Sport         | cycling | volleyball  | biathlon | climbing   |

