.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda, sprite
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, amaryllis, begonia, orchid
There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, italian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, august, june, september
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
 2. the egyptian is the person who growsbegonia##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 4. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the person who growsorchid##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is the italian##1
 8. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the british##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | sprite    | juice      |
| Flower           | begonia | azalea | amaryllis | orchid     |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | italian   | british   | indonesian |
| Birthday           | september         | march       | june  | august       |

