.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
City: venice, san-francisco, new-york, nizza
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, plum, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, sudoku, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, superhero, musical, disaster
 1. the person traveling to venice is the person eating corn##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 7. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 9. the person watching musical movies is the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person traveling to new-york is the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| City   | nizza       | new-york   | venice   | san-francisco   |
| Food       | lime        | zucchini | corn    | plum       |
| Hobby      | woodworking | chess    | sudoku  | card-games |
| Movie-Genre      | superhero  | musical  | horror | disaster    |

