.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, bird, goldfish
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, motorbike, subway, roller
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person driving the subway is between the person who's sport is cricket and the owner of the goldfish##2
 3. the manager is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the librarian is the owner of the lizard##1
 5. the bartender is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 6. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
 7. the owner of the ferret is the bartender##1
 8. the person driving the subway is the librarian##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
10. the librarian is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
12. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Pet    | bird    | goldfish      | lizard          | ferret    |
| Transport   | motorbike | roller       | subway | taxi |
| Job     | musician     | manager      | librarian     | bartender |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | snowboarding | skiing        | cricket   |

