 7. the fan of folk is the person eating cauliflower##1
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| City      | rome  | edinburgh    | berlin       | new-york       |
| Food          | orange    | cauliflower | artichoke | apple     |
