The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, fantasy, sports, zombie
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, nigerian, spanish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee, fanta, milk
 1. the person drinking milk is in an odd position##4
 2. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking fanta##2
 3. the american is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the spanish is on the right of the nigerian##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 8. the fan of folk is on the left of the australian##1
 9. the person drinking cola is between the american and the person watching fantasy movies##2
10. the fan of folk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
11. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the fan of country##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre         | folk  | pop    | country    | jazz |
| Movie-Genre   | sports   | epic       | fantasy  | zombie    |
| Nationality   | american | australian | nigerian | spanish   |
| Beverage           | fanta    | cola        | milk   | coffee    |

