 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 7. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of house is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
13. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
