.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, soul, funk, hip-hop
There are 4 different nationalities: american, thai, british, dutch
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the thai##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 3. the american is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the thai is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 7. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 8. the british is on the far right##1
 9. the thai is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the american##1
11. the dutch is in an odd position##4
12. the fan of reggae is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice       | hot-chocolate | 7up        | milk        |
| Music-Genre         | hip-hop | funk       | reggae | soul |
| Nationality   | dutch     | thai        | american    | british      |
| Sport         | sailing     | volleyball    | water-polo | badminton   |

