.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, pop, techno
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, turquise, apricot, lilac
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, fonseca, pall-mall, aristoff
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the fan of techno is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is between the person who likes coral and the person who likes lilac##2
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 5. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the fan of house is the fonseca-smoker##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 8. the person who likes lilac is in an even position##4
 9. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
10. the person who likes coral is in an even position##4
11. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | ambient | techno     | pop        |
| Color   | apricot | lilac  | turquise     | coral |
| Cigar         | fonseca    | alhambra | pall-mall      | aristoff |
| Transport     | skateboard | car     | helicopter | bike       |

 